a. Attribution.

If You Share the Licensed Material (including in modified form), You must:

i. retain the following if supplied by the Licensor with the Licensed Material: (A) identification of the creator(s) of the Licensed Material and any others designated to receive attribution, in a reasonable manner; (B) the title of the Licensed Material if supplied; (C) notice that the Licensed Material is licensed under this Public License; (D) a link to this Public License; (E) a disclaimer of warranties; and (F) a URI or web link that points to the material if reasonably available;

