iii. indicate the licensed material's author (or authors), an attribution statement, and a link to the license.

b. ShareAlike.

If You Share Adapted Material, You must license the Adapted Material under the same license as the Licensed Material (CC BY-SA 4.0) or a later version.

c. No additional restrictions.

You may not apply legal terms or technological measures that legally restrict others from doing anything the license permits.

